* Although [[Katherine Pryde (Earth-616)|Kitty Pryde]] was acting liaison to the Lights for a time, [[Hope Summers (Earth-616)|Hope]] made it clear she was not part of the team and was to serve in a purely advisory capacity.{{r|Generation Hope #6}}

