| Trivia                  = 
* The [[X-Men (Earth-616)|X-Men]] were first made aware of the Lights in {{cl|X-Men: Second Coming #2}}, the first Light appeared on panel in {{cl|Uncanny X-Men #526}}, worked as a team through much of {{cl|Uncanny X-Men #526}}-{{cl|Uncanny X-Men #529|529}} and {{cl|Generation Hope #1}}-{{cl|Generation Hope #4|4}} , and they became an officially sanctioned X-Team with [[Scott Summers (Earth-616)|Cyclops]]' permission in {{cl|Generation Hope #5}}.

* Many of The Lights come from the same geographic regions or nations as the ''All New, All Different'' [[X-Men (Earth-616)|X-Men]] team:
**[[Hope Summers (Earth-616)|Hope Summers]] and [[Scott Summers (Earth-616)|Cyclops]] were both born in [[Alaska (State)|Alaska]].
**[[Laurie Tromette (Earth-616)|Laurie Tromette]] and [[James Howlett (Earth-616)|Wolverine]] were both discovered in [[Canada]].
**[[Idie Okonkwo (Earth-616)|Idie Okonkwo]] and [[Ororo Munroe (Earth-616)|Storm]] both come from [[Africa]] though from [[Nigeria]] and [[Kenya]] respectively.
**[[Teon Macik (Earth-616)|Teon]] originally comes from [[Ukraine]] while [[Piotr Rasputin (Earth-616)|Colossus]] comes from [[Russia]].
**Both [[Kenji Uedo (Earth-616)|Kenji Uedo]] and [[Shiro Yoshida (Earth-616)|Sunfire]] are [[Japan]] natives.
**[[Sixth Light (Earth-616)|''Sixth Light'']] was born in [[Berlin]], [[Germany]]{{r|Generation Hope #6}} and [[Kurt Wagner (Earth-616)|Nightcrawler]] hails from Germany.
**[[Gabriel Cohuelo (Earth-616)|Gabriel Cohuelo]] born and raised in [[Mexico City]] and (though it is a weak connection) [[John Proudstar (Earth-616)|Thunderbird]] was from an [[Camp Verde|Apache reservation]] in [[Arizona (State)|Arizona]] in the American southwest.
**[[Zeeshan (Earth-616)|Zeeshan]] was discovered in [[United Kingdom]] while [[Sean Cassidy (Earth-616)|Banshee]] was born in [[Ireland]].

* [[Megan Gwynn (Earth-616)|Pixie]], [[Martha Johansson (Earth-616)|No-Girl]], and [[Sebastian Shaw (Earth-616)|Sebastian Shaw]] were the only members of the team to have their powers prior to [[Decimation|M-Day]].
